</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-64_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-65_ pf-text-1"><strong>Invest in training</strong> - Continuous professional development ensures that care workers know the latest best practices in person-centred care.

